data.description: Do not miss this beautiful split level all brick home in Village Green! 5 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs, 2 family rooms downstairs, Living room, dining area and kitchen on the main floor! No carpet in this house, hardwood, laminate or tile. The kitchen has granite counters, tile backsplash, stainless steel applainces and opens to the dining area! The family/bonus rooms on the lower level give plenty of space for enteraining ro providing an office or playroom for the kids! 2 car attached side loa garage with large driveway. Fenced back yard is ready for a family get together. New downstairs HVAC in 5/2022 and new upstairs system in 7/2022. HOA & Pool optional.
